        <para id="id9089756">It seems to me that once an institution commits through a supportive IP policy — the growth in FORE is impressive. A good example is Otago Polytechnic in new Zealand. They have implemented a new IP policy where all resources default to a CC-BY license. Since the implementation of this policy — free content development at the <link url="http://wikieducator.org/Otago_Polytechnic" window="new">Otago Polytechnic</link> has been prolific and inspiring.</para>
        <para id="id9100882">Great post Derek — thanks. Wayne</para>
      </section>
