        <title>13. Wayne Mackintosh - June 3rd, 2008 at 3:31 pm </title>
        <para id="id9097037">Hey Derek,</para>
        <para id="id9097044">Knowing the values underpinning freedom and what freedom means, is going to be the cornerstone of future success of FORE — as RMS says, we need to know what freedom means because “freedom is easily lost.”</para>
        <para id="id9097059">Thanks for the link to Archbishop Tutu’s opening at the Digital Freedom Exposition. By way of example I’ve attempted to illustrate the velocity of free content growth. Thanks to a CC-BY-SA license — WikiEducator is able to enrich the learning experience of our community by incorporating the video into our tutorial on <link url="http://wikieducator.org/Wikieducator_tutorial/What_is_free_content/Free_content_defined" window="new">free content</link>.</para>
        <para id="id9097086">Thanks Derek for an inspiring contribution.</para>
